      • doStressTest

        public void doStressTest(int ntrials,
                         int nnodes)
        Run a stress test.

        Note: You may run out of heap space during the test for large branching factors when combined with a large #of nodes.

        Parameters:
        ntrials - The #of trials. Each trial has a random slotSize and branchingFactor. 50% of the trials (on average) will use record compression.
        nnodes - The #of random nodes per trial.
